  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO PROVIDE AN INCOME TAX CREDIT FOR CERTAIN SMALL EMPLOYERS OFFERING THEIR EMPLOYEES AN INDIVIDUAL COVERAGE HEALTH REIMBURSEMENT ARRANGEMENT (ICHRA) IN LIEU OF A TRADITIONAL EMPLOYER-PROVIDED HEALTH INSURANCE PLAN; TO PROVIDE THE AMOUNT OF THE CREDIT; TO PROVIDE A REPORTING REQUIREMENT TO THE DEPARTMENT OF REVENUE; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
